
combine
 *1 1/2 cup grated onions
 *2 beaten eggs
 *1/2 cup milk
 *1/3 cup parsley
 *1 tsp dry mustard
 *1 tsp salt
 *1/2 tsp cinnamon
 *1/2 tsp nutmeg
 *1/2 tsp clove
 *1/2 tsp pepper
 *1/4 tsp ginger
combine with
 *3 lbs ground beef pork veal
combine with
 *1 cup breadcrumbs

---------------
this is the original recipe
you can double all the spices

